query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_posicoes,
  COUNT(DISTINCT wl.code) as enderecos_distintos,
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.sku) as produtos_distintos
FROM inventory i
JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
WHERE i.tenantId = 1149002;
